<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{أتى}</span> قرب <span class="c3">{أمر الله}</span> وهو الساعه<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
